00:36:21.844 --> 00:36:24.525
ker nihče ne ve,
kako dolgo bo to trajalo.

00:36:24.648 --> 00:36:26.835
Tvoj humor ni smešen.

00:36:27.070 --> 00:36:30.485
Moti me, medtem ko jem,
Michelle pa tudi.

00:36:30.547 --> 00:36:34.436
Prosim utihni in pojejmo v miru.

