Michelle, poslušaj me.
Ne stori tega!

00:41:46.978 --> 00:41:48.869
Pomagajte nam.

00:41:50.329 --> 00:41:52.735
Neka ženska je zunaj.
-Odpri vrata.

00:41:53.525 --> 00:41:55.891
Rada bi šla noter.

00:41:55.954 --> 00:41:58.179
Videti je poškodovana.
Želi, da jo spustim noter.

00:41:58.224 --> 00:42:00.777
Ne spuščaj je noter!

00:42:00.862 --> 00:42:02.641
Poglej njen obraz, Michelle!

00:42:02.764 --> 00:42:07.081
Ne, ne, ne...

00:42:07.204 --> 00:42:10.657
Pomagaj mi, z mano je vse v redu.

00:42:10.804 --> 00:42:14.320
Res sem dobro.
Prosim, dobro sem.

00:42:14.688 --> 00:42:19.632
Samo malo me spusti noter.
Prosim, odpri vrata.

00:42:19.780 --> 00:42:20.882
Odpri jih.

00:42:20.960 --> 00:42:25.094
Roti me. -Ne moreš ji pomagati.
Nihče ji ne more.

00:42:25.152 --> 00:42:27.112
Z mano bo vse v redu.

00:42:27.259 --> 00:42:30.724
Dobro bom, samo spusti me noter.

00:42:31.380 --> 00:42:32.634
Odpri vrata!

00:42:32.673 --> 00:42:33.818
Ne poslušaj je!

00:42:33.891 --> 00:42:36.786
